294
00:16:30,420 --> 00:16:31,530
I'll be there soon.

295
00:16:35,050 --> 00:16:36,410
Let's have another round.

296
00:16:37,700 --> 00:16:41,020
(Yue)

297
00:16:41,450 --> 00:16:42,290
Hello? Yue.

298
00:16:42,890 --> 00:16:43,800
Hello? Director Qin,

299
00:16:44,010 --> 00:16:45,050
when will you arrive?

300
00:16:45,770 --> 00:16:46,720
I'll be there soon.

301
00:16:51,920 --> 00:16:53,170
- Yue.
- Director Qin.

302
00:16:53,410 --> 00:16:55,130
I have to be away for a bit.

303
00:16:55,170 --> 00:16:56,170
Can you look after my kid for me?

304
00:16:56,170 --> 00:16:57,010
I'll be back very soon.

305
00:16:57,010 --> 00:16:58,250
What is so urgent?

306
00:16:59,370 --> 00:17:00,210
Help me look after Ziyuan.

307
00:17:00,290 --> 00:17:01,200
I'll be back very soon.

308
00:17:08,560 --> 00:17:10,160
Sir, the house is on fire!

309
00:17:12,290 --> 00:17:14,010
What are you doing?

310
00:17:14,010 --> 00:17:15,690
Are you trying to become an immortal?

311
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:18,050
The house is almost on fire.

312
00:17:20,450 --> 00:17:21,640
My wife went out to have fun.

313
00:17:21,970 --> 00:17:23,050
She doesn't care about me either.

314
00:17:23,320 --> 00:17:25,290
I need to eat, right?

315
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:27,290
If you can't cook,

316
00:17:27,290 --> 00:17:28,880
then order takeout.

317
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:30,530
You can't set the house on fire!

318
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:32,120
I can't order takeout.

319
00:17:32,120 --> 00:17:33,010
Moreover,

320
00:17:33,250 --> 00:17:34,250
I don't love eating the food

321
00:17:34,450 --> 00:17:35,400
that others cook.

322
00:17:36,010 --> 00:17:36,880
My wife can cook,

323
00:17:36,880 --> 00:17:38,120
but she doesn't make it for me.

324
00:17:38,600 --> 00:17:39,970
What a selfish wife!

325
00:17:41,360 --> 00:17:42,970
You are going too far.

326
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:44,010
You can't do anything.

327
00:17:44,010 --> 00:17:45,450
But you are still so picky.

328
00:17:45,560 --> 00:17:47,120
Your wife spoiled you.

329
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:49,050
This is what she should do.

330
00:17:49,770 --> 00:17:50,800
She has become like this now

331
00:17:50,800 --> 00:17:52,160
because my daughter-in-law

332
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:53,250
has influenced her badly.

333
00:17:55,120 --> 00:17:56,320
If you keep doing this,

334
00:17:57,490 --> 00:17:58,930
no one will take care of you in the future.

335
00:17:58,930 --> 00:17:59,770
I won't eat.

336
00:18:01,320 --> 00:18:02,320
I am not the same.

337
00:18:02,970 --> 00:18:04,210
I am getting paid

338
00:18:04,210 --> 00:18:05,690
to work for you.

339
00:18:05,690 --> 00:18:07,010
But your wife does everything

340
00:18:07,010 --> 00:18:08,290
every day for free.

341
00:18:08,450 --> 00:18:09,600
But she still has to endure anger.

342
00:18:10,010 --> 00:18:11,690
Sooner or later she will stop working.

343
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:12,640
How dare she!

344
00:18:13,320 --> 00:18:14,210
Anyway,

345
00:18:14,840 --> 00:18:16,450
she is the wife of the Hu family.

346
00:18:16,770 --> 00:18:18,210
The wife of the Hu family?

347
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:19,360
What's so great about it?

348
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:21,290
Royal relatives?

349
00:18:25,800 --> 00:18:27,010
My previous employer,

350
00:18:27,010 --> 00:18:28,250
the husband treats his wife

351
00:18:28,250 --> 00:18:30,010
just like you treat your wife.

352
00:18:30,050 --> 00:18:31,050
He extends a hand

353
00:18:31,050 --> 00:18:32,290
for everything.

354
00:18:32,530 --> 00:18:34,730
Later, he made his wife run away due to anger.

355
00:18:35,450 --> 00:18:37,160
Then he was home alone.

356
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:39,010
One day,

357
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:40,600
when he was alone at home,

358
00:18:41,360 --> 00:18:43,970
suddenly he had a sharp pain in his heart,

359
00:18:44,840 --> 00:18:45,800
then he just...

360
00:18:48,080 --> 00:18:48,920
What happened?

361
00:18:49,450 --> 00:18:50,290
Dead?

362
00:18:50,800 --> 00:18:51,840
He can do anything now.

363
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:54,360
What the hell!

364
00:18:54,770 --> 00:18:55,610
Eat an orange.

365
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:58,560
There's one more thing.

366
00:18:58,560 --> 00:19:00,840
I saw a real story online a couple of days ago.

367
00:19:00,840 --> 00:19:02,400
Is everything you said earlier fake?

368
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,450
There is an old lady.

369
00:19:04,970 --> 00:19:05,930
She can't

370
00:19:05,930 --> 00:19:07,210
stand her husband

371
00:19:07,210 --> 00:19:08,880
bossing her around all day long.

372
00:19:09,560 --> 00:19:11,530
In a fit of anger, she ran away from home.

373
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:14,050
She drove alone on a self-guided tour.

374
00:19:14,250 --> 00:19:15,560
Over the course of two or three years,

375
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:17,730
she traveled around most of China,

376
00:19:18,120 --> 00:19:19,880
leaving her husband alone at home.

377
00:19:20,120 --> 00:19:21,930
It's been really tough.

378
00:19:24,290 --> 00:19:26,640
Why did these misfortunes happen to men?

379
00:19:26,740 --> 00:19:28,070
Bad deeds are rewarded with bad results.

380
00:19:28,450 --> 00:19:30,010
- Well...
- He deserves it.

381
00:19:33,730 --> 00:19:34,970
You can't do anything at all.

382
00:19:34,970 --> 00:19:36,360
You should have a bit of backbone.

383
00:19:36,390 --> 00:19:37,530
You just learn to cook on your own.

384
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:38,440
Right?

385
00:19:38,640 --> 00:19:39,480
Or

386
00:19:39,770 --> 00:19:41,400
you face everyone with a smile.

387
00:19:41,600 --> 00:19:42,800
How could all the benefits

388
00:19:42,800 --> 00:19:44,400
be enjoyed by you alone?

389
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:45,320
So

390
00:19:45,320 --> 00:19:47,050
you need to think this through.

391
00:19:47,320 --> 00:19:49,800
Who really can't live without whom?

392
00:19:51,770 --> 00:19:53,360
I'm really afraid of you.

393
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:55,490
I am not scary at all.

394
00:20:13,010 --> 00:20:14,080
Mom, how's it?

395
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:15,080
Not bad, right?

396
00:20:15,320 --> 00:20:16,600
This apartment is ready to move in.

397
00:20:16,600 --> 00:20:17,600
Everything is prepared for us.

398
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:18,600
We don't need to bring anything.

399
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:20,080
It's really quite complete.

400
00:20:20,080 --> 00:20:21,050
It's enough for the three of us

401
00:20:21,050 --> 00:20:22,210
to live here.

402
00:20:23,930 --> 00:20:25,050
What do you mean?

403
00:20:27,290 --> 00:20:28,770
Leave myself a way out.

404
00:20:28,970 --> 00:20:29,880
Just in case.

405
00:20:31,210 --> 00:20:33,010
What's going on between you and Cheng?

406
00:20:37,320 --> 00:20:38,160
Mom,

407
00:20:39,250 --> 00:20:40,600
don't worry about me.

408
00:20:40,930 --> 00:20:42,320
I will handle it myself.

409
00:20:44,250 --> 00:20:45,800
If Hu Cheng calls you

410
00:20:46,160 --> 00:20:47,800
or if anyone calls you,

411
00:20:48,320 --> 00:20:49,250
don't contact,

412
00:20:49,250 --> 00:20:50,120
don't answer.

413
00:20:52,490 --> 00:20:53,800
If the nursing home calls me,

414
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:55,010
I will do as you said.

415
00:21:13,530 --> 00:21:14,370
Hello?

416
00:21:15,250 --> 00:21:16,210
Well,

417
00:21:16,210 --> 00:21:17,880
when can you come back?

418
00:21:18,290 --> 00:21:20,160
I haven't finished class yet.

419
00:21:22,120 --> 00:21:24,120
I can't cook.

420
00:21:26,290 --> 00:21:27,640
I mean,

421
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:30,210
after you get back,

422
00:21:30,360 --> 00:21:31,770
teach me.

423
00:21:32,490 --> 00:21:33,770
Let's talk after the class.

424
00:21:44,320 --> 00:21:45,160
You finally returned.

425
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:46,560
Why were you in such a hurry just now?

426
00:21:46,770 --> 00:21:47,610
Jiaojiao.

427
00:21:48,560 --> 00:21:49,770
It seems

428
00:21:49,770 --> 00:21:51,360
they like you a lot.

429
00:21:51,500 --> 00:21:53,250
You could consider it a side job now.

430
00:21:54,970 --> 00:21:56,730
Just now a staff member

431
00:21:56,730 --> 00:21:58,490
helped me with the toys

432
00:21:58,600 --> 00:21:59,800
and water.

433
00:21:59,800 --> 00:22:01,160
Otherwise, I

434
00:22:01,250 --> 00:22:02,640
can't handle both of them alone.

435
00:22:02,800 --> 00:22:03,730
She's here.

436
00:22:04,120 --> 00:22:06,050
Tired of playing? Don't keep bothering him.

437
00:22:06,050 --> 00:22:07,160
Drink some water.

438
00:22:07,340 --> 00:22:08,290
Ok.

439
00:22:08,290 --> 00:22:09,230
Thank you.

440
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:10,770
If you need anything, just call me.

441
00:22:10,970 --> 00:22:11,810
Ok.

442
00:22:13,560 --> 00:22:14,600
It's like a banana.

443
00:22:17,320 --> 00:22:18,800
We'll come here next time.

444
00:22:19,210 --> 00:22:20,560
Are you happy today?

445
00:22:20,560 --> 00:22:21,400
Happy.

446
00:22:32,080 --> 00:22:33,600
- The bear is coming.
- Attack him.

447
00:22:33,930 --> 00:22:35,010
Jiaojiao! Protect Jiaojiao!

448
00:22:35,010 --> 00:22:36,530
- Protect Jiaojiao.
- Jiaojiao, come on.

449
00:22:44,560 --> 00:22:47,730
(Gulliver's Travels)
Every time I want to go

450
00:22:48,160 --> 00:22:49,490
to the town to take a look, I always sit

451
00:22:49,490 --> 00:22:51,970
in this small "cabin" used for traveling.

452
00:22:52,160 --> 00:22:54,690
Glumdalclitch

453
00:22:54,690 --> 00:22:56,560
put the "cabin" on my lap

454
00:22:56,840 --> 00:22:58,560
and placed me on his knee,

455
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:03,160
sitting in a type of open sedan.

456
00:23:03,930 --> 00:23:05,400
Four people carry us...

457
00:23:15,210 --> 00:23:17,120
...followed by two spies of the queen behind.

458
00:23:17,120 --> 00:23:18,080
Ziyuan.

459
00:23:19,080 --> 00:23:20,530
- I'm back.
- Dad.

460
00:23:20,530 --> 00:23:21,770
You are back!

461
00:23:38,730 --> 00:23:40,290
Mom is telling me a story.

462
00:23:40,290 --> 00:23:41,930
Mom is telling you a story, huh?

463
00:23:43,450 --> 00:23:44,290
Come here.

464
00:23:45,120 --> 00:23:46,160
Let me tell you one.

465
00:23:46,450 --> 00:23:48,010
Let Dad tell you for a while.

466
00:23:48,600 --> 00:23:49,560
Where were we?

467
00:23:50,560 --> 00:23:52,010
Here.

468
00:23:56,770 --> 00:23:57,680
Here?

469
00:23:58,770 --> 00:24:01,480
I want to go to the town to take a look,

470
00:24:02,140 --> 00:24:03,940
I always sit

471
00:24:04,100 --> 00:24:05,140
in this small "cabin"

472
00:24:05,700 --> 00:24:07,380
used for traveling.

473
00:24:15,220 --> 00:24:16,060
Mr. Feng,

474
00:24:16,380 --> 00:24:17,860
what we are talking about now is

475
00:24:18,140 --> 00:24:19,940
your relationship with Chen Pingzhang.

476
00:24:21,460 --> 00:24:23,340
The key issue you need to tell me is this.

477
00:24:25,180 --> 00:24:26,620
I know, Ms. Luo.

478
00:24:27,820 --> 00:24:28,860
He Kuan's matter

479
00:24:28,860 --> 00:24:30,620
is also related to the Purchasing Department.

480
00:24:30,820 --> 00:24:32,060
And the problem is even more serious.

481
00:24:33,220 --> 00:24:34,920
You want to talk to me about He Kuan?

482
00:24:36,180 --> 00:24:37,570
Let me reiterate to you once again.

483
00:24:38,060 --> 00:24:39,340
About Chen Pingzhang,

484
00:24:39,820 --> 00:24:41,220
do you have anything else to add?

485
00:24:43,580 --> 00:24:44,620
Nothing to add for now.

486
00:24:44,700 --> 00:24:45,860
I need to think about it again.

487
00:24:50,140 --> 00:24:52,300
You better think it over.

488
00:24:53,100 --> 00:24:54,820
If it gets discovered later,

489
00:24:54,820 --> 00:24:56,020
this's not such a simple conversation

490
00:24:56,020 --> 00:24:57,580
between you and me.

491
00:25:14,220 --> 00:25:16,020
Keep a close eye on the Technical Department.

492
00:25:16,620 --> 00:25:18,380
This is our first software launch.

493
00:25:18,540 --> 00:25:19,940
We must not have any issues.

494
00:25:20,420 --> 00:25:21,260
Besides,

495
00:25:21,380 --> 00:25:22,540
prepare several backup plans

496
00:25:22,900 --> 00:25:24,180
to avoid chaos

497
00:25:24,180 --> 00:25:25,180
when there are loopholes.

498
00:25:25,780 --> 00:25:26,620
I'm keeping an eye on it.

499
00:25:26,860 --> 00:25:27,700
There is still time.

500
00:25:30,020 --> 00:25:30,860
In short,

501
00:25:31,940 --> 00:25:34,540
no issues can arise before the contract

502
00:25:35,660 --> 00:25:37,580
with Xianbin Capital is signed.

503
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:41,260
Don't worry.

504
00:25:50,540 --> 00:25:51,380
By the way,

505
00:25:52,140 --> 00:25:53,140
there's something

506
00:25:53,900 --> 00:25:55,420
I'm quite worried about you as well.

507
00:25:57,060 --> 00:25:58,180
Previously, you used your own money

508
00:25:58,180 --> 00:25:59,460
to fill in the company.

509
00:26:00,860 --> 00:26:03,060
You haven't transferred the money back.

510
00:26:03,700 --> 00:26:05,140
Does Yue know about this?

511
00:26:08,600 --> 00:26:09,940
Apples and oranges.

512
00:26:11,220 --> 00:26:12,580
Don't let Yue worry.

513
00:26:26,620 --> 00:26:27,760
Yue hasn't come again today.

514
00:26:32,220 --> 00:26:33,060
I knew it.

515
00:26:33,460 --> 00:26:34,780
Yue is so capable.

516
00:26:34,860 --> 00:26:36,580
She must have found a better job.

517
00:26:38,020 --> 00:26:39,700
What job is better than a lawyer?

518
00:26:40,860 --> 00:26:41,700
Make a copy of it.

519
00:26:42,060 --> 00:26:43,380
You make me copy again!

520
00:27:07,140 --> 00:27:09,020
If the legal assistant assigned by Party B

521
00:27:09,020 --> 00:27:10,540
no longer provides services to Party A

522
00:27:10,540 --> 00:27:11,860
or voluntarily resigns,

523
00:27:11,860 --> 00:27:13,860
the legal assistant appointed by Party B

524
00:27:13,860 --> 00:27:15,540
promises to mortgage the house as collateral.

525
00:27:15,660 --> 00:27:17,140
I modified this contract myself.

526
00:27:17,300 --> 00:27:19,580
I just want to express my sincerity.

527
00:27:19,580 --> 00:27:21,140
I know that the work you've been doing

528
00:27:21,220 --> 00:27:22,780
is not about the investigation.

529
00:27:22,780 --> 00:27:24,300
Regarding Licheng Anping,

530
00:27:24,380 --> 00:27:26,180
if you know anything,

531
00:27:26,540 --> 00:27:28,460
please let me know.

532
00:27:28,460 --> 00:27:30,700
Yue, what exactly is Licheng Anping?

533
00:27:33,180 --> 00:27:35,340
Yue, you have any plans now, right?

534
00:27:36,100 --> 00:27:37,420
But I think

535
00:27:37,420 --> 00:27:38,860
this plan is very dangerous.

536
00:27:44,860 --> 00:27:48,620
(Yue)

537
00:28:04,780 --> 00:28:05,900
Today I will join you

538
00:28:05,900 --> 00:28:07,180
for the kindergarten activities.

539
00:28:08,860 --> 00:28:10,140
Aren't you going to work?

540
00:28:10,820 --> 00:28:13,060
I think being with family is more important.

541
00:28:15,220 --> 00:28:16,060
Honey.

542
00:28:18,180 --> 00:28:19,140
I know

543
00:28:19,580 --> 00:28:20,860
you are tired of the old clothes.

544
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:22,420
I ordered a new set for you.

545
00:28:40,180 --> 00:28:41,220
This embroidery

546
00:28:41,300 --> 00:28:42,220
and this craftsmanship

547
00:28:43,660 --> 00:28:44,940
are so exquisite.

548
00:28:47,060 --> 00:28:47,940
A wife

549
00:28:48,220 --> 00:28:49,780
is the face of a family.

550
00:28:50,300 --> 00:28:51,780
Of course I have to treat you with care.

551
00:28:53,860 --> 00:28:54,700
Honey,

552
00:28:56,180 --> 00:28:57,900
you really care about me, don't you?

553
00:29:11,300 --> 00:29:12,140
Mrs. Hu,

554
00:29:12,220 --> 00:29:14,580
you look so beautiful in that cheongsam.

555
00:29:14,660 --> 00:29:16,420
Yes, it's really pretty.

556
00:29:16,420 --> 00:29:18,460
Your figure is really good. I'm so envious.

557
00:29:19,220 --> 00:29:20,060
Thank you.

558
00:29:20,340 --> 00:29:22,100
My mom is a little fairy.

559
00:29:30,300 --> 00:29:31,180
So you already knew

560
00:29:31,180 --> 00:29:32,540
