561
00:29:33,460 --> 00:29:35,380
This is Ziyuan's favorite game.

562
00:29:52,820 --> 00:29:53,700
Is it?

563
00:29:53,780 --> 00:29:55,300
Hello, Mr. Hu, Mrs. Hu.

564
00:29:55,700 --> 00:29:57,620
The next round of the game is about to start.

565
00:29:57,620 --> 00:29:58,580
Please come with me.

566
00:29:58,580 --> 00:29:59,420
Ziyuan.

567
00:29:59,420 --> 00:30:00,340
You go there first.

568
00:30:01,540 --> 00:30:02,380
Follow me.

569
00:30:14,660 --> 00:30:15,500
Slow down.

570
00:30:17,540 --> 00:30:18,860
Mom, Dad,

571
00:30:19,100 --> 00:30:20,460
I am here.

572
00:30:23,390 --> 00:30:24,250
What's wrong?

573
00:30:24,260 --> 00:30:25,180
Ms. Li,

574
00:30:26,300 --> 00:30:27,780
every time we play this game,

575
00:30:28,100 --> 00:30:29,940
Dad always blindfolds Mom,

576
00:30:29,940 --> 00:30:31,060
